lan motorcycle Grand Prix|2013 Catalan Grand Prix]]\n| Next_year's_race = [[2015 Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix|2015 Catalan Grand Prix]]\n}}\n\n[[Category:2014 MotoGP race reports|Catalan Grand Prix]]\n[[Category:2014 in Spanish motorsport|Catalan Motorcycle Grand Prix]]\n[[Category:2014 in Catalan sport|motorcycle]]\n[[Category:Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix]]\n[[Category:June 2014 sports events in Europe|Catalan motorcycle Grand Prix]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Grand Prix motorcycle race report\n| Grand Prix = Catalan\n| flag = Spain\n| Official_Name = Gran Premi [[Monster Energy]] de Catalunya<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.motorsportmagazine.com/database/races/2014-catalan-motogp|title=2014 Catalan MotoGP|date=13 June 2017|website=Motorsportmagazine.com|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref>\n| Location = [[Circuit de Barcelona-Catalunya]]\n| Image = CatalunyaMotoGP.svg\n| Course_mi = 2.937\n| Course_km = 4.727\n| Race_No = 7\n| Season_No = 18\n| Date = 15 June\n| Year = 2014\n|Pole_Rider_MotoGP          = [[Dani Pedrosa]]\n|Pole_Rider_MotoGP_Country  = Spain\n|Pole_Rider_MotoGP_Bike     = [[Honda]]\n|Pole_Time_MotoGP           = 1:40.985\n|Fast_Rider_MotoGP          = [[Marc M\u00e1rquez]]\n|Fast_Rider_MotoGP_Country  = Spain\n|Fast_Rider_MotoGP_Bike     = [[Honda]]\n|Fast_Time_MotoGP           = 1:42.182 on lap 2\n|First_Rider_MotoGP         = [[Marc M\u00e1rquez]]\n|First_Rider_MotoGP_Country = Spain\n|First_Rider_MotoGP_Bike    = [[Honda]]\n|Second_Rider_MotoGP        = [[Valentino Rossi]]\n|Second_Rider_MotoGP_Country= Italy\n|Second_Rider_MotoGP_Bike   = [[Yamaha Motor Company|Yamaha]]\n|Third_Rider_MotoGP         = [[Dani Pedrosa]]\n|Third_Rider_MotoGP_Country = Spain\n|Third_Rider_MotoGP_Bike    = [[Honda]]\n|Pole_Rider_Moto2           = [[Esteve Rabat]]\n|Pole_Rider_Moto2_Country   = Spain\n|Pole_Rider_Moto2_Bike      = [[Kalex]]\n|Pole_Time_Moto2            = 1:46.569\n|Fast_Rider_Moto2           = [[Esteve Rabat]] \n|Fast_Rider_Moto2_Country   = Spain\n|Fast_