 Racing Team|Caterham]] [[Eskil Suter|Suter]]\n|Pole_Time_Moto2            = 2:07.094\n|Fast_Rider_Moto2           = [[Esteve Rabat]]\n|Fast_Rider_Moto2_Country   = Spain\n|Fast_Rider_Moto2_Bike      = [[Kalex]]\n|Fast_Time_Moto2            = 2:07.253 on lap 15\n|First_Rider_Moto2          = [[Esteve Rabat]]\n|First_Rider_Moto2_Country  = Spain\n|First_Rider_Moto2_Bike     = [[Kalex]]\n|Second_Rider_Moto2         = [[Mika Kallio]]\n|Second_Rider_Moto2_Country = Finland\n|Second_Rider_Moto2_Bike    = [[Kalex]]\n|Third_Rider_Moto2          = [[Maverick Vi\u00f1ales]]\n|Third_Rider_Moto2_Country  = Spain\n|Third_Rider_Moto2_Bike     = [[Kalex]]\n|Pole_Rider_Moto3           = [[\u00c1lex Rins]]\n|Pole_Rider_Moto3_Country   = Spain\n|Pole_Rider_Moto3_Bike      = [[Honda]]\n|Pole_Time_Moto3            = 2:13.112\n|Fast_Rider_Moto3           = [[Jakub Kornfeil]]\n|Fast_Rider_Moto3_Country   = Czech Republic\n|Fast_Rider_Moto3_Bike      = [[KTM]]\n|Fast_Time_Moto3            = 2:13.664 on lap 5\n|First_Rider_Moto3          = [[\u00c1lex Rins]]\n|First_Rider_Moto3_Country  = Spain\n|First_Rider_Moto3_Bike     = [[Honda]]\n|Second_Rider_Moto3         = [[\u00c1lex M\u00e1rquez]]\n|Second_Rider_Moto3_Country = Spain\n|Second_Rider_Moto3_Bike    = [[Honda]]\n|Third_Rider_Moto3          = [[Enea Bastianini]]\n|Third_Rider_Moto3_Country  = Italy\n|Third_Rider_Moto3_Bike     = [[KTM]]\n}}\n\nThe '''2014 British motorcycle Grand Prix''' was the twelfth round of the [[2014 Grand Prix motorcycle racing season]]. It was held at the [[Silverstone Circuit]] in [[Silverstone]] on 31 August 2014.\n\n[[File:Jorge Lorenzo, Marc M\u00e1rquez and Valentino Rossi 2014 Silverstone.jpeg|thumb|Jorge Lorenzo, Marc M\u00e1rquez and Valentino Rossi, celebrating on the podium after finishing second, first and third in the MotoGP race.]]\n\n==Classification==\n===MotoGP===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n! Pos.\n! No.\n! Rider\n! Team\n! Manufacturer\n! Laps\n! Time/Retired\n! Grid\