{"title_page": "Riverside station (Ottawa)", "text_new": "{{Infobox station \n| name          = Riverside\n| style         = OC Transpo\n| type          = [[Transitway (Ottawa)|Transitway]] station\n| image         = riversidestn.jpg\n| image_size    = \n| image_caption = \n| address       = \n| coordinates   = {{Coord|45|23|47.5|N|75|40|10|W|display=inline,title}}\n| line          = <!-- line information is detailed under \"services\" --> \n| other         = \n| structure     = \n| platform      = 2\n| depth         = \n| levels        = 2\n| tracks        = \n| parking       = No\n| bicycle       = No\n| baggage_check = \n| opened        = 1991\n| closed        = \n| rebuilt       = \n| electrified   = \n| ADA           = \n| code          = \n| owned         = [[OC Transpo]]\n| zone          = \n| former        = \n| passengers    = \n| pass_year     = \n| pass_percent  = \n| pass_system   = \n| mpassengers   = \n| services      = {{adjstn|system=OC Transpo\n|line1=Route 97|left1=Pleasant Park|right1=Smyth\n|line2=Route 98|left2=Pleasant Park|right2=Smyth\n|line3=Route 99|left3=Pleasant Park|right3=Smyth}}\n| map_locator   = \n}}\n\n'''Riverside ''' is an [[OC Transpo]] bus station on Ottawa's [[Ottawa Rapid Transit|Transitway]] that is connected to the [[Riverside Hospital of Ottawa|Riverside Campus]] of [[The Ottawa Hospital]] near the intersection of Smyth Road and [[Riverside Drive (Ottawa)|Riverside Drive]]. Stairs and elevators from the platform level lead directly to the interior of the hospital, making bus travel easy for medical appointments even in bad weather.\n\nThe hospital is the primary trip generator and main purpose for this station. There are no connecting bus routes here.\n\nThe station was built when the hospital underwent a major expansion of its facility. It agreed to let the transitway pass in its terrain and open a new station as there were initially no stations to be built at that location. The 4,200 square feet new administration wing and Transit station was completed in 1991.[http://onlinepubs.trb.org/onlinepubs/tcrp/tcrp_rpt_16-4.pdf]\n\n==Service==\n{{see also|OC Transpo routes}}\n\nThe following routes serve Riverside:<br>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\"|Riverside Station Service\n|-\n| '''Rapid routes''' || {{rbox|97||#{{octc|rapid}}}} {{rbox|98||#{{octc|rapid}}}} {{rbox|99||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|rapid}}}}\n|-\n| '''Frequent routes''' || {{rbox|10||#{{octc|frequent}}}} {{rbox|40||white;border:1px solid #{{octc|frequent}}|#{{octc|frequent}}}} {{rbox|88||#{{octc|frequent}}}} {{rbox|90||#{{octc|frequent}}}}\n|-\n| '''Local routes''' || {{rbox|48||#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|49||#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|92||#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|93||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|96||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|190||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}} {{rbox|199||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}}\n|-\n| '''Connexion routes''' || {{rbox|290||#{{octc|connexion}}}} {{rbox|291||#{{octc|connexion}}}} {{rbox|294||#{{octc|connexion}}}} {{rbox|299||#{{octc|connexion}}}}\n|-\n| '''Event routes''' || {{rbox|451||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}}\n|-\n| '''School routes''' || {{rbox|613||white;border:1px solid #{{octc|school}}|#{{octc|school}}}}\n|}\n\n=== Notes ===\n* Routes {{rbox|40||white;border:1px solid #{{octc|frequent}}|#{{octc|frequent}}}}, {{rbox|93||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}}, {{rbox|96||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}}, {{rbox|99||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|rapid}}}} and {{rbox|199||white;border:1px solid black|#{{octc|local}}}} serve this station during peak periods only.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n{{unreferenced|date=August 2014}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.ottawahospital.on.ca Ottawa Hospital]\n*[http://www.octranspo.com/mapscheds/transitway/station_layout_pdf/RIV.pdf OC Transpo station page]\n*[http://www.octranspo.com/mapscheds/transitwa